---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="About - Matt Wright" description="Learn more about Matt Wright, founder of EVM Systems and builder of agentic infrastructure.">
  <Header />

  <main class="flex-1 py-12">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="divider-thick mb-8"></div>

        <h1 class="font-grotesk text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          MATT WRIGHT
        </h1>

        <div class="divider-thin mb-4"></div>
        <p class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-wider">
          FOUNDER · BUILDER · WEB3 + AI
        </p>
        <div class="divider-thin mt-4"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="font-inter text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
          I build infrastructure for the agent economy.
        </p>

        <p class="font-inter text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I'm the founder of <strong>EVM Systems</strong>, where we're building the coordination layer for autonomous agents. Our flagship products — <strong>Gaia</strong> (agent coordination protocol) and <strong>AgentWork</strong> (agent marketplace) — are designed for a future where AI agents outnumber humans in the workforce.
        </p>

        <p class="font-inter text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Before this, I spent years deep in the EVM ecosystem, building smart contract infrastructure and tooling for web3 applications. I believe the convergence of crypto and AI is one of the most important technological shifts of our time.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-grotesk text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">What I'm Working On</h2>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>EVM Systems</strong> — Infrastructure for autonomous agent coordination
          </li>
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>Gaia</strong> — Protocol for multi-agent collaboration and economic coordination
          </li>
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>AgentWork</strong> — Marketplace where agents bid on tasks and coordinate work
          </li>
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>Agent Identity Systems</strong> — SOUL.md and AGENTS.md frameworks for persistent agent identity
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-grotesk text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">My Beliefs</h2>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            AI agents will outnumber humans in the workforce within 5 years
          </li>
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            The agent economy needs open infrastructure, not closed platforms
          </li>
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            Web3 + AI convergence is inevitable and necessary
          </li>
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            Building in public creates better products and stronger communities
          </li>
          <li class="font-inter text-lg">
            Autonomous systems need identity, memory, and constraints to be trustworthy
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-grotesk text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Connect</h2>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>ENS:</strong> <a href="https://app.ens.domains/mattwright.eth" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber underline hover:no-underline">mattwright.eth</a>
          </p>
          <p class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>Twitter:</strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/mattwright_eth" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber underline hover:no-underline">@mattwright_eth</a>
          </p>
          <p class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>Farcaster:</strong> <a href="https://warpcast.com/mattwright.eth" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber underline hover:no-underline">mattwright.eth</a>
          </p>
          <p class="font-inter text-lg">
            <strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/MateoDev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber underline hover:no-underline">MateoDev</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 border-4 border-dead-black bg-white">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm mb-2">
            💼 OPEN TO:
          </p>
          <ul class="font-inter text-base space-y-2">
            <li>• Collaboration on agent infrastructure projects</li>
            <li>• Speaking at web3/AI conferences and events</li>
            <li>• Advisory roles for agentic systems companies</li>
            <li>• Interesting conversations about the future</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t-4 border-dead-black">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-block font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-amber transition-colors"
        >
          ← BACK HOME
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  .prose a {
    @apply text-amber underline hover:no-underline;
  }
</style>
